        Please be informed that your request for amendment was reverted due to <%= "#{@approval_comment}" %>. The details are as follows: <br>
    <% else %>
        Foreign Worker Amendment details as follows: <br>
    <% end %>

    <% if @foreign_worker.approval_status == "UPDATE_APPROVED" %>
        <i>Dimaklumkan permohonan Pindaan Maklumat Pekerja Asing anda telah berjaya. Maklumat adalah seperti berikut:</i>
